#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Index.factorize.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Index.factorize"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:1 of
msgid "Encode the object as an enumerated type or categorical variable."
msgstr "将对象编码为枚举类型或分类变量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:3 of
msgid ""
"This method is useful for obtaining a numeric representation of an array "
"when all that matters is identifying distinct values. `factorize` is "
"available as both a top-level function :func:`pandas.factorize`, and as a"
" method :meth:`Series.factorize` and :meth:`Index.factorize`."
msgstr ""
"当只需要识别不同值时，此方法对于获取数组的数值表示很有用。`factorize` 既"
"可作为顶级函数 :func:`pandas.factorize` 使用，也可作为方法 :meth:`Series."
"factorize` 和 :meth:`Index.factorize` 使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:8 of
msgid ""
"A 1-D sequence. Sequences that aren't pandas objects are coerced to "
"ndarrays before factorization."
msgstr "一维序列。非pandas对象的序列在因子化之前会被强制转换为ndarrays。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:11 of
msgid "Sort `uniques` and shuffle `codes` to maintain the relationship."
msgstr "对`uniques`进行排序并打乱`codes`以保持关系。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:14 of
msgid ""
"If True, the sentinel -1 will be used for NaN values. If False, NaN "
"values will be encoded as non-negative integers and will not drop the NaN"
" from the uniques of the values."
msgstr ""
"如果为True，将使用-1作为NaN值的标记。如果为False，NaN值将被编码为非负整数"
"，并且不会从值的唯一值中删除NaN。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:19 of
msgid ""
"* **codes** (*ndarray*) -- An integer ndarray that's an indexer into "
"`uniques`.   ``uniques.take(codes)`` will have the same values as "
"`values`. * **uniques** (*ndarray, Index, or Categorical*) -- The unique "
"valid values. When `values` is Categorical, `uniques`   is a Categorical."
" When `values` is some other pandas object, an   `Index` is returned. "
"Otherwise, a 1-D ndarray is returned.    .. note::       Even if there's "
"a missing value in `values`, `uniques` will      *not* contain an entry "
"for it."
msgstr ""
"* **codes** (*ndarray*) -- 用作`uniques`索引器的整数ndarray。   ``uniques"
".take(codes)`` 将具有与`values`相同的值。 * **uniques** (*ndarray, Index,"
" 或 Categorical*) -- 唯一的有效值。当`values`是Categorical时，`uniques`  "
" 是Categorical。当`values`是其他pandas对象时，返回   `Index`。否则，返回"
"一维ndarray。    .. note::       即使`values`中有缺失值，`uniques`也     "
" *不*会为其包含条目。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:19 of
msgid ""
"**codes** (*ndarray*) -- An integer ndarray that's an indexer into "
"`uniques`. ``uniques.take(codes)`` will have the same values as `values`."
msgstr ""
"**codes** (*ndarray*) -- 用作`uniques`索引器的整数ndarray。``uniques.take"
"(codes)``将具有与`values`相同的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:21 of
msgid ""
"**uniques** (*ndarray, Index, or Categorical*) -- The unique valid "
"values. When `values` is Categorical, `uniques` is a Categorical. When "
"`values` is some other pandas object, an `Index` is returned. Otherwise, "
"a 1-D ndarray is returned."
msgstr ""
"**uniques** (*ndarray, Index, 或 Categorical*) -- 唯一的有效值。当`values"
"`是Categorical时，`uniques`是 Categorical。当`values`是其他pandas对象时，"
"返回`Index`。否则，返回一维ndarray。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:27 of
msgid ""
"Even if there's a missing value in `values`, `uniques` will *not* contain"
" an entry for it."
msgstr "即使`values`中有缺失值，`uniques`也*不会*为其包含条目。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`cut`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:33 of
msgid "Discretize continuous-valued array."
msgstr "离散化连续值数组。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`unique`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:36 of
msgid "Find the unique value in an array."
msgstr "在数组中查找唯一值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:39 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:40 of
msgid "Reference :ref:`the user guide <reshaping.factorize>` for more examples."
msgstr "参考 :ref:`用户指南 <reshaping.factorize>` 获取更多示例。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:43 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:44 of
msgid ""
"These examples all show factorize as a top-level method like "
"``pd.factorize(values)``. The results are identical for methods like "
":meth:`Series.factorize`."
msgstr ""
"这些示例都显示了factorize作为顶级方法，如 ``pd.factorize(values)``。对于"
"像 :meth:`Series.factorize` 这样的方法，结果是相同的。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:56 of
msgid ""
"With ``sort=True``, the `uniques` will be sorted, and `codes` will be "
"shuffled so that the relationship is the maintained."
msgstr "使用 ``sort=True``，`uniques`将被排序，`codes`将被打乱以保持关系。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:66 of
msgid ""
"When ``use_na_sentinel=True`` (the default), missing values are indicated"
" in the `codes` with the sentinel value ``-1`` and missing values are not"
" included in `uniques`."
msgstr ""
"当 ``use_na_sentinel=True`` (默认值)时，缺失值在`codes`中用标记值 ``-1`` "
"表示，缺失值不会包含在 `uniques`中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:76 of
msgid ""
"Thus far, we've only factorized lists (which are internally coerced to "
"NumPy arrays). When factorizing pandas objects, the type of `uniques` "
"will differ. For Categoricals, a `Categorical` is returned."
msgstr ""
"到目前为止，我们只对列表进行了因子化(内部被强制转换为NumPy数组)。在对"
"pandas对象进行因子化时，`uniques`的类型会有所不同。对于 Categoricals，"
"返回`Categorical`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:88 of
msgid ""
"Notice that ``'b'`` is in ``uniques.categories``, despite not being "
"present in ``cat.values``."
msgstr "注意，尽管``'b'``不在``cat.values``中，但它在``uniques.categories``中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:91 of
msgid ""
"For all other pandas objects, an Index of the appropriate type is "
"returned."
msgstr "对于所有其他pandas对象，返回适当类型的Index。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.factorize.factorize:101 of
msgid ""
"If NaN is in the values, and we want to include NaN in the uniques of the"
" values, it can be achieved by setting ``use_na_sentinel=False``."
msgstr ""
"如果值中包含NaN，并且我们希望在值的唯一值中包含NaN，可以通过设置 ``use_na"
"_sentinel=False`` 来实现。"
